# Coding Standards

## Components

- All components use `"use client"` directive (animations and interactivity require it)
- Functional components with default exports
- Image component from `next/image` for all images (with proper `sizes` prop)
- Framer Motion for scroll-triggered animations (`whileInView` with `viewport={{ once: true }}`)

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS v4 with CSS variables defined in `globals.css` using `@theme inline`
- Custom colors referenced as `text-foreground`, `text-muted`, `bg-card`, `border-border`, etc.
- No inline styles except for animation delays
- Responsive: mobile-first with `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` breakpoints

## Framer Motion

- Use `as const` for ease values in variants to satisfy TypeScript (e.g., `ease: "easeOut" as const`)
- `AnimatePresence` with `mode="popLayout"` for filter transitions
- Keep animation durations subtle: 0.2-0.6s range

## Content Language

- All user-facing text must be in **Russian**
- Brand name "borisRozin" stays in Latin script
- Alt text for images should be in Russian
